WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.190 --> 00:00:02.730
"Mewalk" ilovasi uchun biz amalga 
oshirgan so‘nggi kodlash vazifasi 

00:00:02.730 --> 00:00:06.190
media ijro etuvchi resurslarini endi kerak 
bo‘lmasdanoq tezda bo‘shatish bilan bog‘liq edi.

00:00:06.190 --> 00:00:10.020
Ammo har doim ham audio fayl tugallanadi 
deb taxmin qila olmaymiz.

00:00:10.020 --> 00:00:13.605
Agar foydalanuvchi boshqa faoliyatga 
o‘tishiga xalaqit bersa, biz hamma narsani 

00:00:13.605 --> 00:00:16.935
to‘g‘ri tozalashga ishonch 
hosil qilishimiz kerak.

00:00:16.935 --> 00:00:19.995
Sizga savolim shuki, agar foydalanuvchi 
o‘z faoliyatini tashlab qo‘ysa,

00:00:19.995 --> 00:00:24.055
"MediaPlayer" tomonidan ishlatiladigan 

00:00:24.055 --> 00:00:25.785
resurslarning qaysi siklini bajarish kerak?

00:00:25.785 --> 00:00:30.870
Bu "onResume", "onCreate", "OnStop" yoki 
"onDestroy" metodlarida bo‘ladimi? Shunday qilib,

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:34.930
siz tanlovni amalga oshirganingizdan 
so‘ng, ilovalarni o‘zgartiring, 

00:00:34.930 --> 00:00:39.110
shunda biz resurslarni haqiqatan 
ham chiqaramiz ushbu hayot sikli bosqichida.

00:00:39.110 --> 00:00:42.250
Shunday qilib, ushbu kodni o‘zgartirishdan
oldin va keyin sizning ilovangiz 

00:00:42.250 --> 00:00:44.490
qanday ko‘rinishda 
bo‘lishini sizga aytib beray.

00:00:44.490 --> 00:00:46.730
Ilovangiz hozirda shunday ishlaydi.

00:00:46.730 --> 00:00:50.027
Agar biron bir so‘zni bossam, u so‘zni
ovoz chiqarib aytishni boshlaydi,

00:00:50.027 --> 00:00:52.703
va harakatni tugatmasdan qoldirsam,
ilova hali ham to‘liq audio faylni 

00:00:52.703 --> 00:00:55.649
tinglashni davom ettiradi.

00:00:55.649 --> 00:00:57.530
[BLANK_AUDIO]

00:00:59.520 --> 00:01:02.680
&gt;&gt; Shunday qilib, biz kodning versiyasi,
bu yerda biz hayotiy faoliyat 

00:01:02.680 --> 00:01:05.500
sikliga muvofiq media manbalarni 
to‘g‘ri tozalashimiz kerak.

00:01:05.500 --> 00:01:08.820
Bu holda qurilmaning uy 
tugmachasini bosganimizda,

00:01:08.820 --> 00:01:11.820
Ilova audio faylni, hatto so‘zning 
o‘rtasida bo‘lsa ham, 

00:01:11.820 --> 00:01:13.290
darhol tinglashni to‘xtatishi kerak.

00:01:13.290 --> 00:01:16.290
Bu ovozni foydalanuvchi bizning 
ilova ichida bo‘lganida 

00:01:16.290 --> 00:01:18.180
tinglashimiz kerakligini tasdiqlaydi.

00:01:18.180 --> 00:01:21.780
Chunki, hozirgi vaziyatda biz musiqa yoki 
podkast pleyer dasturi hisoblanamiz.

00:01:21.780 --> 00:01:24.054
Shunday qilib, sizga 
namoyish qilib ko‘rsatay.

00:01:24.054 --> 00:01:25.471
[SOUND].

00:01:25.471 --> 00:01:28.140
Yaxshisi, oldinga o‘tib, 
kodni hozir o‘zgartiring.

00:01:28.140 --> 00:01:30.650
Va barcha to‘rtta faoliyatimizni 
yangilashni unutmang.

